author: Kate Dries on The Slot, shared by Joanna Rothkopf to Jezebel
title: We're Off to DC for Inauguration Weekend
text:
Go to permalink American suffragette marchers on their way from New Jersey to Washington DC at the time of Woodrow Wilson’s inauguration in February of 1913. Image via Topical Press Agency/ Getty . 
What happens when you put 11 women and one man into two cars headed straight for an inevitable traffic clusterfuck? We’re about to find out. Advertisement 
That’s right, Jezebel staff members will be heading to DC tomorrow for both Friday’s Inauguration of President-elect Donald Trump, and the decidedly more interesting Women’s March on Washington Saturday. Expect dispatches throughout the weekend, and as usual, please .
